Interface Entity

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AnimalVehicle, ArmorStand, Arrow, Bat, Blaze, Boat, CaveSpider, ChestMinecart, Chicken, ChickenEgg, CommandBlockMinecart, ContainerMinecart, Cow, Creeper, EmptyMinecart, EnderCrystal, EnderDragon, EnderEye, Enderman, Endermite, EnderPearl, EntityAnimal, EntityItem, EntityLiving, EntityMob, EntityPotion, EntityThrowable, FallingBlock, Fireball, FireworkRocket, FishHook, FurnaceMinecart, Ghast, GiantZombie, Golem, Guardian, HangingEntity, HopperMinecart, Horse, Human, IronGolem, ItemFrame, LargeFireball, LeashKnot, LightningBolt, LivingBase, MagmaCube, Minecart, MobSpawnerMinecart, Mooshroom, NonPlayableCharacter, Ocelot, Painting, Pig, PigZombie, Player, Projectile, Rabbit, Sheep, Silverfish, Skeleton, Slime, SmallFireball, Snowball, Snowman, Spider, Squid, Tameable, TNTMinecart, TNTPrimed, Vehicle, Villager, WeatherEffect, Witch, Wither, WitherSkull, Wolf, XPBottle, XPOrb, Zombie

    public interface Entity
    This defines an entity in the world Everything that is not a block inherits from Entity in a way.
    Author:
    Chris (damagefilter), Jason (darkdiplomat), Larry1123
